name: 2 Tier 'Birds & the Bees' White Art Deco Vintage Cupcake Stand
description:
This gorgeous cake stand has two tiers that comprise of a vintage square white cake plate with grass and flowers on the bottom, followed by a smaller square art deco plate featuring birds and flowers on top.

All plates are in great vintage condition, and are lovingly sourced and transformed by myself, any questions or enquiries please just ask :)

name: 3 Tier 'Harry's' Gold & Green Vintage Cupcake Stand
description:
This gorgeous cake stand has three tiers that comprise of a vintage 'exclusive to Harrods' plate on the bottom, followed by a small Gold Royal Worcester Porcelain side plate, and a Gold Royal Worcester Porcelain ramekin on top.

All plates are in great vintage condition, and are lovingly sourced and transformed by myself, any questions or enquiries please just ask :)

name: 3 Tier 'Breakfast at Tiffanys' White Floral Teacup Cupcake Stand
description:
This gorgeous cake stand has three tiers that comprise of a vintage floral cake plate on the bottom, followed by a small side plate with a bolder print of flowers, and a cute tiny little cup and saucer from a 'breakfast set' on top (which gave me inspiration for the name).

All plates are in great vintage condition, and are lovingly sourced and transformed by myself, any questions or enquiries please just ask :)

name: 2 Tier 'Orange Flash' Cream & Gold Vintage Cupcake Stand
description:
This gorgeous cake stand has two tiers that comprise of matching  vintage plates, with the larger square cake plate on the bottom, followed by a round side plate on top. The plates are cream with gold edges, with little orange flashes or streaks.

All plates are in great vintage condition, and are lovingly sourced and transformed by myself, any questions or enquiries please just ask :)
